description:
Video credits: Phil Chen - Ted Greene conducting a seminar at California Vintage Guitar. This is part 7 of a lengthy (2 hours worth of footage) multi-segment master class. Sharpen your pencils and stay attentive... CLASS IS IN SESSION with the Chord Chemist Ted Greene as he covers many aspects of Jazz, Blues, Solo Guitar, Rock, Chord Changes, Chord Substitutions and many musical surprises.

Simply AMAZING!!!

Visit http://www.tedgreene.com for all things Ted
fulltitle: Ted Greene Seminar - California Vintage Guitar 5-18-03 part 7
